name: Coherence Of The Feminine Inner Being

metadata.name: Embracing The Feminine Inner Being
metadata.description:
She is embracing and welcoming her Feminine Inner Being. She enters this process ready and willing to be fragile and face any insecurities and emotional wounds.
As she fully allows and integrates this aspect of herself, the woman can live authentically and with devotion. She reminds us, men and women, of the essence of truly embracing the fullness of our feminine nature, which is a source of power and creativity.
